Connect via WebSocket. After connect, send JSON messages:

• Send message:
  {"type":"MESSAGE","content":"Hello!"}

• Typing indicator:
  {"type":"TYPING","isTyping":true}

• Mark read:
  {"type":"READ"}

Server events received:
• {"type":"HISTORY","messages":[...]}  — on connect
• {"type":"MESSAGE_SENT","messageId":"..."}  — confirm
• {"type":"TYPING","senderType":"worker","isTyping":true}
• {"type":"READ_RECEIPT","readerId":"..."}

